This button is an "over-simplified" version of a similar button added by the [url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tab-mix-plus/]Tab Mix Plus add-on[/url]. It creates a button with a menu listing all recently closed tabs from which can be restored each tab individually or all at once.

